net.myorb.math.primenumbers

  • Packages that use net.myorb.math.primenumbers 
    Package Description
    net.myorb.math.expressions.algorithms
    Implementations of algorithms that provide for evaluation of expression primitives.
    net.myorb.math.expressions.controls
    Control layer for the CalcLib application including selection of the base type for a run.
    net.myorb.math.expressions.managers
    Implementation of the Space Management interface for the supported data types (Integer, Real, Complex).
    net.myorb.math.primenumbers
    Implementations of algorithms supporting prime number use and factorization in particular.
    net.myorb.math.primenumbers.sieves
    Implementations of algorithms supporting prime number sieve use (Eratosthenes, Sundaram).
    net.myorb.testing
    Implementations of algorithms supporting CalcLib unit tests.
    net.myorb.testing.squareRoot
